welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Caloundra, a charming coastal town known for its pristine beaches and relaxed atmosphere. We are delighted to have you here and invite you to explore and experience all that our beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Caloundra Airport handles all commercial flights and services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Caloundra Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1

terminals.name: Terminal 2

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
